{
  "description": "A wide-angle shot capturing a bustling maritime scene with a large cargo ship partially visible on the right edge of the frame. The foreground is dominated by a deep blue body of water with gentle waves. In the middle ground, a modern, white and blue passenger ferry is traveling towards the viewer, surrounded by smaller boats, including a red and white rescue boat and a sailboat. The background features a series of bridges spanning the water, creating a layered perspective. The most prominent bridge appears to be a suspension bridge with tall towers and a complex network of cables. Further in the distance, hazy hills or mountains are visible, adding depth to the scene. The overall lighting suggests a bright, sunny day with some atmospheric haze.",
